### Backend Structure (`/BackEnd`)
The backend is structured geographically by feature/purpose.

- **`index.js`**: The main entry point. Sets up the Express server, applies middleware (CORS, body-parser), and mounts all router endpoints (`/student`, `/admin`, `/admission`, `/course`, `/`). Starts the server on port `5000`.
- **`mangodb.js`**: Contains the MongoDB connection logic using `mongoose` and environment variables.
- **`models/`**: Mongoose schemas defining the database collections.
  - `admin.js`: Schema for administrators.
  - `Student.js`: Schema for students.
  - `courseDetais.js`: Schema for courses.
  - `attendence.js`: Schema, likely for tracking attendance mappings.
  - `admission/`: Contains specific schemas related to the admission processes.
- **`routes/`**: Express routers handling API endpoints.
  - `adminAuth.js` (Prefix `/admin`): Handles admin login, registration, and management.
  - `studentAuth.js` (Prefix `/student`): Handles student authentication and profile access.
  - `admission.js` (Prefix `/admission`): Handles new admission applications and records.
  - `courseDetails.js` (Prefix `/course`): Endpoints for fetching / updating course information.
  - `attendence.js` (Prefix `/`): Handles attendance logs and updates.
- **`middlewear/`**: Custom Express middlewares for authorization and request validation.
  - `fetchAdmin.js`: Middleware to verify Admin JWT tokens.
  - `fetchStudent.js`: Middleware to verify Student JWT tokens.
- **Scripts**: Auxiliary scripts for system setup and maintenance (e.g., `createNewAdmin.js`, `updateAdminPassword.js`, `fixAdminPasswords.js`, `updateAllAdmins.js`).

### Frontend Structure (`/FrontEnd`)
The frontend is built using standard Vite+React templates, designed with modular functional components.

- **`index.html`** & **`main.jsx`**: The React DOM root mounts here.
- **`App.jsx`**: Main application component, generally setting up the routing structure.
- **`src/pages/`**: Contains top-level page components mapped to routes.
  - `Home.jsx`, `About.jsx`, `Courses.jsx`, `Examination.jsx`, `Achievement.jsx`, `Profile.jsx`, `Activity.jsx`
- **`src/components/`**: Modular, reusable UI components split by feature sections.
  - **`Admission/`**: Components specifically for the admission flows.
  - **`OnlyAdmin/`**: Components restricted to users with Admin privileges (e.g., admin dashboards, data tables).
  - **`Profile/`**, **`Home/`**, **`Examination/`**, **`Activity/`**: Dedicated sub-components for their respective pages.
- **`src/contexts/`**: React Context files for managing global state.
- **Styles & Configs**: Includes `tailwind.config.js`, `postcss.config.js`, `vite.config.js`, and `App.css` for styling and building.

